    "description": {
      "value": "<div class=\"rd__b  rd__b--3\"><p>You create a bonfire on ground that you can see within range. Until the spell ends, the magic bonfire fills a 5-foot cube. Any creature in the bonfire's space when you cast the spell must succeed on a Dexterity saving throw or take [[/damage 1d8 type=fire]] damage. A creature must also make the saving throw when it moves into the bonfire's space for the first time on a turn or ends its turn there.</p><p>The bonfire ignites flammable objects in its area that aren't being worn or carried.</p><p>The spell's damage increases by [[/damage 1d8]] when you reach 5th level ([[/damage 2d8]]), 11th level ([[/damage 3d8]]), and 17th level ([[/damage 4d8]]).</p></div>",
